Interface UserManager.ILoginOperationResponseListener

  • Enclosing class:
    UserManager

    public static interface UserManager.ILoginOperationResponseListener
    The listener interface for receiving ILoginOperationResponse events. The class that is interested in processing a ILoginOperationResponse event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addILoginOperationResponseListener method. When the ILoginOperationResponse event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    See Also:
    ILoginOperationResponseEvent
